{"id": "lyr_5Y-25YCp5paH_MzgzMQ_0003", "text": "共你分手以後 將多了空虛", "structure": {"line_index": 3, "char_count": 11}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 5, 3, 9, 5, 2, 3, 3, 5, 3, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["gung6", "nei5", "fan1", "sau2", "ji5", "hau6", "zoeng1", "do1", "liu5", "hung1", "heoi1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "共", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "分手", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "以後", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "將", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "多", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "了", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "空虛", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "福氣", "artists": ["葉倩文"], "lyricists": ["林振強"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_3831", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5Y-25YCp5paH_MzgzMQ_0002", "next_line_id": "lyr_5Y-25YCp5paH_MzgzMQ_0004", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5Y-25YCp5paH_MzgzMQ_0004", "text": "但延和席必有聚散 風必需要吹", "structure": {"line_index": 4, "char_count": 13}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 0, 0, 2, 3, 5, 2, 9, 3, 3, 3, 4, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["daan6", "jin4", "wo4", "zik6", "bit1", "jau5", "zeoi6", "saan2", "fung1", "bit1", "seoi1", "jiu3", "ceoi1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "但", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "延和席", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "必有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "聚散", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "風必", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "需要", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "吹", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "福氣", "artists": ["葉倩文"], "lyricists": ["林振強"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_3831", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5Y-25YCp5paH_MzgzMQ_0003", "next_line_id": "lyr_5Y-25YCp5paH_MzgzMQ_0005", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5Y-25YCp5paH_MzgzMQ_0005", "text": "河水必須流 朋友你不須帶淚", "structure": {"line_index": 5, "char_count": 12}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 9, 3, 3, 0, 0, 5, 5, 3, 3, 4, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ho4", "seoi2", "bit1", "seoi1", "lau4", "pang4", "jau5", "nei5", "bat1", "seoi1", "daai3", "leoi6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "河水", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "必須", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "流", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "朋友", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不須", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "帶淚", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "福氣", "artists": ["葉倩文"], "lyricists": ["林振強"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_3831", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5Y-25YCp5paH_MzgzMQ_0004", "next_line_id": "lyr_5Y-25YCp5paH_MzgzMQ_0006", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5Y-25YCp5paH_MzgzMQ_0006", "text": "人何處不再聚 好比山與水", "structure": {"line_index": 6, "char_count": 11}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 0, 3, 4, 2, 9, 9, 3, 5, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jan4", "ho4", "bat1", "zoi3", "zeoi6", "hou2", "bei2", "saan1", "jyu5", "seoi2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "人", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "何處", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不再", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "聚", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "好比", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "山", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "與", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "水", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "福氣", "artists": ["葉倩文"], "lyricists": ["林振強"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_3831", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5Y-25YCp5paH_MzgzMQ_0005", "next_line_id": "lyr_5Y-25YCp5paH_MzgzMQ_0007", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5Y-25YCp5paH_MzgzMQ_0007", "text": "若愛得真那慛 有別離有聚", "structure": {"line_index": 7, "char_count": 11}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 4, 3, 3, 5, 5, 2, 0, 5, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["joek6", "oi3", "dak1", "zan1", "naa5", "jau5", "bit6", "lei4", "jau5", "zeoi6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "若愛得", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "真", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "那", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "慛", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "別離", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "有聚", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "福氣", "artists": ["葉倩文"], "lyricists": ["林振強"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_3831", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5Y-25YCp5paH_MzgzMQ_0006", "next_line_id": "lyr_5Y-25YCp5paH_MzgzMQ_0008", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5Y-25YCp5paH_MzgzMQ_0008", "text": "是從前令今天可貴 雖分不告吹", "structure": {"line_index": 8, "char_count": 13}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 0, 0, 2, 3, 3, 9, 4, 3, 3, 3, 4, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["si6", "cung4", "cin4", "ling6", "gam1", "tin1", "ho2", "gwai3", "seoi1", "fan1", "bat1", "gou3", "ceoi1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "從前", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "令", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "今天", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "可貴", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "雖分", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "告吹", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "福氣", "artists": ["葉倩文"], "lyricists": ["林振強"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_3831", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5Y-25YCp5paH_MzgzMQ_0007", "next_line_id": "lyr_5Y-25YCp5paH_MzgzMQ_0009", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
